
-------------------------------------------------------------2- example ----------------------------------------------------------
In the first example, we changed the type of the /etc/named folder and subfolders. But you can give access to only one folder /etc/named/dynamic .
In configuration files /etc/named.conf
it was possible to set specific paths for dns configs by looking at the semanage fcontext -l utility

